          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Puneet</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Puneet is a serial entrepreneur with a proven track record of building and scaling technology companies. His deep understanding of business operations and customer needs drives Summit Craft's customer-centric approach.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              With experience leading teams at both startups and Fortune 500 companies, Puneet brings strategic vision and operational excellence to every AI solution we build. He's passionate about making AI accessible and valuable for businesses of all sizes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
